[33.802466, "o", "le']} at {reminder['time']}\")\r\n    else:\r\n        print(\"No upcoming meetings in the next 15-75 minutes."]
[33.802498, "o", "\")\r\n\r\nif __name__ == '__main__':\r\n    main()\r\nEOF\r\n\u001b[?2004h"]
